roughton]]\n*[[Church Gresley]]\n*[[Clay Cross]]\n*[[Clowne]]\n*[[Coal Aston]]\n*[[Coddington, Derbyshire|Coddington]]\n*[[Codnor]]\n*[[Loscoe|Codnor Breach]]\n*[[Combs, Derbyshire|Combs]]\n*[[Common Side]]\n*[[Common End, Derbyshire|Common End]]\n*[[Conksbury]]\n*[[Coplow Dale]]\n*[[Corbriggs]]\n*[[Cotmanhay]]\n*[[Coton in the Elms]]\n*[[Cowerslane]]\n*[[Cowley, Derbyshire|Cowley]]\n*[[Coxbench]]\n*[[Cressbrook]]\n*[[Creswell, Derbyshire|Creswell]]\n*[[Creswell Model Village]]\n*[[Crich]]\n*[[Cromford]]\n*[[Cross Hill, Derbyshire|Cross Hill]]\n*[[Cross o' th' Hands]]\n*[[Crowden, Derbyshire|Crowden]]\n*[[Crowdecote]]\n*[[Curbar]]\n*[[Cutthorpe]]\n}}\n\n==D==\n{{flatlist|\n*[[Daisy Bank]]\n*[[Dalbury]]\n*[[Dalbury Lees]]\n*[[Dale Abbey|Dale]]\n*[[Dale Abbey]]\n*[[Dale End, Derbyshire|Dale End]]\n*[[Dale Abbey|Dale Moor]]\n*[[Dalebank]]\n*[[Dalebrook]]\n*[[Danesmoor]]\n*[[Darley Bridge]]\n*[[Darley Dale]]\n*[[Darley Hillside]]\n*[[Denby]]\n*[[Denby Bottles]]\n*[[Denby#Related hamlets|Denby Common]]\n*[[Derby]]\n*[[Derwent, Derbyshire|Derwent]]\n*[[Derwent Reservoir (Derbyshire)|Derwent Reservoir]]\n*[[Derwentmouth]]\n*[[River Derwent, Derbyshire|River Derwent]]\n*[[Dethick]]\n*[[Dimple, Derbyshire|Dimple]]\n*[[Dinting]]\n*[[Dinting Vale]]\n*[[Smalley, Derbyshire|Dobholes]]\n*[[Doe Lea]]\n*[[Ashover|Doehole]]\n*[[Dove Head]]\n*[[Dove Holes]]\n*[[Dovedale]]\n*[[Doveridge]]\n*[[Dowlow]]\n*[[Drakelow]]\n*[[Draycott, Derbyshire|Draycott]]\n*[[Dronfield]]\n*[[Dronfield Woodhouse]]\n*[[Duckmanton]]\n*[[Duffield, Derbyshire|Duffield]]\n*[[Duffieldbank]]\n*[[Dunsa]]\n*[[Chesterfield|Dunston]]\n}}\n\n==E==\n{{flatlist|\n*[[Birchover|Eagle Tor]]\n*[[Earl Sterndale]]\n*[[Eastmoor, Derbyshire|Eastmoor]]\n*[[Eaves Knoll]]\n*[[Eckington, Derbyshire|Eckington]]\n*[[Edale]]\n*[[Eddlestow]]\n*[[Edensor]]\n*[[Edlaston]]\n*[[Ednaston]]\n*[[Egginton]]\n*[[Egstow]]\n*[[Elmton]]\n*[[Elmton Common]]\n*[[Elton, Derbyshire|Elton]]\n*[[Elvaston, Derbyshire|Elvaston]]\n*[[Emmett Carr]]\n*[[Etwa