lal (film)|Mohanlal]]||[[Malayalam language|Malayalam]] ||[[Tony Joseph Pallivathukal]]\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Award\n!Category\n!Film\n!Result\n|-\n|2009\n|[[Filmfare Awards South]]\n|[[Filmfare Award for Best Supporting Actress \u2013 Kannada|Best Supporting Actress \u2013 Kannada]]\n|''[[Josh (2009 Kannada film)|Josh]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"9\" |2011\n| rowspan=\"3\" |[[Filmfare Awards South]]\n|[[Filmfare Award for Best Supporting Actress \u2013 Malayalam|Best Supporting Actress \u2013 Malayalam]]\n|''[[Urumi (film)|Urumi]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[Filmfare Award for Best Actress \u2013 Telugu|Best Actress \u2013 Telugu]]\n| rowspan=\"7\" |''[[Ala Modalaindi]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[Filmfare Award for Best Female Playback Singer \u2013 Telugu|Best Female Playback Singer \u2013 Telugu]] (for song ''\"Ammammo Ammo\"'')\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[1st South Indian International Movie Awards]]\n|Best Female Debutant \u2013 Telugu\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|Best Female Playback Singer \u2013 Telugu(for song ''\"Ammammo Ammo\"'')\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[Nandi Awards]]\n|[[Nandi Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n|Hyderabad Times Film Awards\n|Promising Newcomer Female\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n|Ugadi Puraskar Awards\n|Best Actress\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n|[[Vijay Awards]]\n|[[Vijay Award for Best Actress|Best Actress]]\n|''[[180 (2011 Indian film)|Nootrenbandhu]]''\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |2012\n|[[CineMAA Awards]]\n|[[CineMAA Awards|Best Actress (Jury)]]\n|''[[Ishq (2012 film)|Ishq]]''\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n|[[2nd South Indian International Movie Awards]]\n|Rising Star of South Indian Cinema (Female)\n| -\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2013\n|[[Filmfare Awards South]]\n|[[Filmfare Award for Best Actress \u2013 Telugu|Best Actress \u2013 Telugu]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |''[[Gunde Jaari Gallanthayyinde]]''\n|{{Won}}\n|-\n|[[3rd South Indian International Movie Awards]]\n|Best Actress \u2013 Telugu\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|[[Vanitha Film Awards]]\n|Best 